#. Translators: Error displayed when inverse cosine value is undefined
#: lib/number.vala:841
msgid "Inverse cosine is undefined for values outside [-1, 1]"
msgstr "ອາກໂກຊິນແມ່ນບໍ່ສາມາດນິຍາມໄດ້ສຳລັບຄ່ານອກຊ່ວງ [-1, 1]"

